<HEADLINE>
<P>
DOUGLAS, RAMS TAKE MORE PUNISHMENT, THIS TIME FROM FANS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Once my anger subsided after watching the latest heavyweight championship 
debacle, it became clear to me what the problem is and what the solution is. 
</P>
<P>
Give the challenger a guaranteed $1 million. Give the champion a guaranteed $2 
million. Give the winner the rest of the purse, be it $30 million, $50 million 
or $100 million. Then you'll see how fast Buster or any other fighter will get 
off the canvas after a knockdown. 
</P>
<P>
SCOTT MAURER 
</P>
<P>
West Los Angeles 
</P>
