made four drug buys in the bar and observed several similar transactions taking 
place, he said. 
</P>
<P>
Bar owner Cecelia Suarez, 44, was arrested and held at the Las Colinas Jail in 
Santee on narcotics charges, Robinson said. Agents from the Department of 
Alcoholic Beverage Control closed the bar after Suarez's arrest, he said. 
</P>
<P>
A search of Suarez's home in the 100 block of 29th Street uncovered more than 
11 pounds of marijuana, $1,260 in cash and two handguns, Robinson said. Agents 
also arrested Reyna Grageda, 29, at the 29th Street house, and she was held at 
the Las Colinas Jail on narcotics charges, he said. 
