<P>
MOORPARK CLINCHES SHARE OF SOCCER TITLE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Shaun Christensen and Billy Kranz each scored three goals and Robert Harris 
added a pair as Moorpark College defeated host Santa Monica, 10-0, in a Western 
State Conference soccer match Friday night. 
</P>
<P>
The victory clinched at least a share of the WSC title for Moorpark (15-0, 10-0 
in conference play), with one conference match remaining. 
</P>
<P>
Christian Costa and Sergio Pizano each had a goal for Moorpark, the 
sixth-ranked team in the state. 
</P>
