Viejo quarterback Tim Snowden, who threw three touchdown passes Friday night, 
rolls out during 21-9 victory over El Toro. ; Photo, Mission Viejo running back 
Erick Fielding returns a kickoff in the first quarter against El Toro. 
CHRISTINE COTTER / Los Angeles Times 
