FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
College projects -- Because of an error in material furnished by the California 
Community Colleges system, a story Friday incorrectly reported the capital 
projects at Orange Coast College to be funded if voters pass Proposition 143. 
OCC would receive $13.7 million for a vocational technology building and a 
central maintenance facility. Rancho Santiago Community College District would 
receive $17.7 million to acquire land for a second campus in Orange. 
</P>
